title: Escapism - You Should Trust Us (2016)
description:
Escapism - You Should Trust Us

This is the second 'release' from Escapism (the first one was just a torrent too). We're an independant electronic band. Share as much as you want! Our music will always be free.

Since the last torrent, we've focussed on a mainly electronic/synthpop sound. I guess we are influenced by Regurgitator, The Chemical Brothers, VNV Nation, Planet Funk, Pendulum, Infected Mushroom, The Bloody Beetroots, Nine Inch Nails, The Dandy Warhols and The Prodigy. There's probably something you'll like in here.
